response.overview: After a misunderstanding between a well-to-do young man and the girl he wanted to marry, he decides to arbitrarily marry the first random girl that will accept him. This proves harder that he he thought, and late at night and groggy, he gets into his house after some trouble and help from the police, only to realize he's not in his house, but trapped in a strange one with a married woman.
response.tagline: A Griffith picture with only one laugh! But that one lasts from the main title to fade-out.
response.title: Wet Paint
